text: El Guásimo is a corregimiento in Donoso District, Colón Province, Panama with a population of 2,843 as of 2010. Its population as of 1990 was 1,992; its population as of 2000 was 2,350. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Colón Province Category:Road-inaccessible communities of Panama
title: El Guásimo, Colón
